00:00:12.949 --> 00:00:18.923
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:29.690 --> 00:00:33.607
What are you cooking?
Chicken Popcorn

00:00:52.172 --> 00:00:54.285
Ingredients required to make Chicken Popcorn

00:00:54.682 --> 00:01:03.659
Chicken, Ginger-Garlic Paste, Corn Flour, Eggs, Coriander, Salt, Turmeric, Red Chilli Powder, Oil

00:01:15.930 --> 00:01:22.840
Take a pan and heat enough oil for deep frying

00:01:30.678 --> 00:01:38.583
Boil a 250 gms of boneless chicken
for 3-4 mins (half boil it)

00:02:01.498 --> 00:02:08.219
Take the chicken into a mixing bowl

00:02:09.794 --> 00:02:18.558
Add 1/2 tsp turmeric, 1 tsp ginger-garlic paste
and some salt for taste

00:02:19.944 --> 00:02:25.640
Add 1 1/2 tsp of red chilli powder

00:02:29.573 --> 00:02:38.152
Add 2 tsp of corn flour and some
coriander leaves

00:02:42.264 --> 00:02:50.096
Add 2 raw eggs and mix well

00:03:25.059 --> 00:03:31.458
Now, deep fry the chicken

00:03:43.138 --> 00:03:49.092
Take the chicken into a serving bowl

